title: Ebro In The Morning - Respect to KRS-One and Big Daddy Kane
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 10/18.

Enjoy the Guru's handling some problems all the way from Scotland and then hop on the train to Real Hip-Hop Station, because the crew is talking Big Daddy Kane vs. KRS-One. 

Article here: https://www.hot97.com/hip-hop-news/featured/the-young-persons-guide-to-krs-one-verzuz-big-daddy-kane/
